channel.title: Forget about freeman dialogue
channel.description: when you go to the bomb screen thing on that tower near the end of surface tension, a hecu solider starts saying forget about freeman we are cutting our losses and stuff. you can hear other soliders shouting in the background and i think some gunshots. its a bit unnessacery considering there was no fighting at that part in opposing force. anybody else noticed?
